         </creation></profileDesc></teiHeader><facsimile><surface><graphic url="http://images.monasterium.net/pics/AT-WStLA/HA-U/WStLA-HA-Urkunden_01492_a_r.jpg"/></surface><surface><graphic url="http://images.monasterium.net/pics/AT-WStLA/HA-U/WStLA-HA-Urkunden_01492_a_v.jpg"/></surface><surface><graphic url="http://images.monasterium.net/pics/AT-WStLA/HA-U/WStLA-HA-Urkunden_01492_b_r.jpg"/></surface><surface><graphic url="http://images.monasterium.net/pics/AT-WStLA/HA-U/WStLA-HA-Urkunden_01492_b_v.jpg"/></surface></facsimile><text><body><div type="abstract" resp="kg"><p><rs type="event" ref="ev__QGW_II_I_1492">* Anno
                  nativitatis ( domini) millesimo quadringentesimo primo, indicione nona, die
                  vicesima quinta. mensis aprilis, hora quasi nona, pontificatus sanctissimi in
                  Christo patris et domini nostri domini Bonifacii, divina providencia pape noni,
                  anno duodecimo, in monte Wissegradensi prope Pragam, in domo prepositure
                  sacrosancte ecclesie beati Petri Wissegradensis montis predicti, in curia domus
                  eiusdem <triggerstring n="disp">entsagt</triggerstring> in Gegenwart des Notars und der
                  Zeugen <rs type="fn" role="issuer">der <rs type="person" ref="pe__wenzel_QGW_II_I_1487"><roleName type="occ" corresp="org__antiochia-dioezese">Patriarch</roleName> von <rs type="org" ref="org__antiochia-dioezese">Antiochia</rs>, <roleName type="occ" corresp="pe__ruprecht_von_der_pfalz_QGW_II_I_1492"><rs type="person" ref="pe__ruprecht_von_der_pfalz_QGW_II_I_1492">königliche
                           Kanzler</rs></roleName> und <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wissegard-st_peter">Propst</roleName> der <rs type="org" ref="org__wissegard-st_peter">Wissehrader Kirche</rs>
                     Wenceslaus</rs></rs>
                  <rs type="fn" role="other"><triggerstring n="fn">aus besonderer Gefälligkeit
                        gegen</triggerstring>
                     <rs type="person" ref="pe__albrecht_herzog_von_oesterreich_QGW_II_I_1020">Herzog Albrecht von Oesterreich</rs></rs>allen Ansprüchen an die <rs type="org" ref="org__nalb-pfarre">Pfarrkirche in Neliv ( Nalib B.) </rs>, zu
                  Gunsten des <rs type="fn" role="recipient"><rs type="person" ref="pe__bartholomaeus_wuerfel_QGW_II_I_1375"><roleName type="occ" corresp="org__nalb-pfarre">Rectors</roleName> derselben Bartholomeus
                        dictus Würffel</rs></rs>. <rs type="fn" role="other"><triggerstring n="fn">Unter den Bevollmächtigten</triggerstring> wird auch <rs type="person" ref="pe__johann_sindram_von_heiligenstadt_QGW_II_I_1492"><roleName type="title">magister</roleName> Johannes Sinderami de Heligenstat</rs>
                     genannt</rs>.</rs>
            </p></div><div type="nota"><p><rs type="event" ref="ev__QGW_II_I_1492"><rs type="fn" role="witness">Notariatssignet
                     und Publicationsclausel des <rs type="person" ref="pe__johann_wlassivis_QGW_II_I_1487">Mathias, quondam Duchconis de
                        Cladna, <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__prag-dioezese">clericus</roleName> Pragensis diocesis, auctoritate imperiali notarius
                        publicus</rs> Angekündigt ist das Siegel des Patriarchen.</rs></rs>
            </p></div><div type="lists"><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/placeList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/personList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/eventList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/orgList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/></div></body></text></TEI>